wiki.summary: "On the Ground" is the debut single by South Korean-New Zealand singer and BLACKPINK member ROSÉ. It was released on March 12, 2021 by YG Entertainment as the lead single from her debut single album, R. The first music video teaser for "On the Ground" was released on 7 March. The song was written by Rosé alongside Amy Allen, Raúl Cubina, Jon Bellion, Jorgen Odegard and Teddy Park, and was produced by the latter three alongside Ojivolta and 24. Read more on Last.fm.
